# Info

Invoked to modify existing creative tabs, allowing you to add or remove items.

# Example

```js
StartupEvents.modifyCreativeTab('minecraft:building_blocks', event => {
	// Add custom blocks to the building blocks tab
	event.add('kubejs:my_block')
	
	// Remove items from the tab
	event.remove('minecraft:dirt')
})

StartupEvents.modifyCreativeTab('minecraft:combat', event => {
	// Add custom weapons
	event.add('kubejs:super_sword')
})
```
